# Default-Deny — Allowlist nur explizite Code+Doc-Pfade

/*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!deploy-manifest.yaml
!.github/
!.github/workflows/
!.github/workflows/**
!Makefile
!apps/
!docs/
!tools/
!cockpit/
!schema/
!workspaces/
workspaces/*
!workspaces/**/
!workspaces/**/*.tf
!workspaces/**/Dockerfile
!workspaces/**/*.sh
!workspaces/**/*.md

apps/**
!apps/**/
!apps/**/*.go
!apps/**/*.mod
!apps/**/*.sum
!apps/**/*.md

tools/*
!tools/*.sh
!tools/twenty/
!tools/twenty/**
!tools/portfolio/
!tools/portfolio/**
# Compiled Go binaries (main-package outputs) — built SHA-pinned on deploy,
# never committed. A committed binary dirties the work tree on rebuild and
# blocks the Merger push (release-pipeline durchstich befund #3).
tools/portfolio/master-kanban/master-kanban
tools/portfolio/adapters/coder/coder
tools/portfolio/adapters/planfile/planfile
tools/portfolio/adapters/solartown/solartown
tools/portfolio/adapters/vibekanban/vibekanban
!tools/deploy/
!tools/deploy/**
# deploy tool binary — built locally on werkstatt, never committed (same rule as
# the portfolio binaries above: a committed binary dirties the tree on rebuild
# and blocks the Merger push).
tools/deploy/deploy
!tools/master-kanban/
!tools/master-kanban/**
!tools/secrets-broker/
!tools/secrets-broker/**
!tools/wp0-frueh-warnung/
!tools/wp0-frueh-warnung/**
!tools/mk-health/
!tools/mk-health/**
!tools/twenty/
!tools/twenty/**

docs/*
!docs/README.md
!docs/vision/
!docs/architecture/
!docs/decisions/
!docs/plans/

**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/node_modules/
**/.next/

# Gas Town (added by gt)
.runtime/
.claude/
.gemini/
.logs/
__pycache__/
state.json
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE.local.md
bin/
